Package: frequencyConnectedness
Type: Package
Title: Spectral decomposition of connectedness measures
Version: 0.1.5
Date: 2015-06-29
Author: Tomas Krehlik
Maintainer: Tomas Krehlik <krehlik@utia.cas.cz>
Description: This package accompanies a paper dedicated to spectral deomposition of connectedness measures and their interpretation. We implement all the developed estimators as well as the historical counterparts.
Depends:
	vars,
	urca,
	parallel
Suggests: 
	testthat,
	stringr,
	mAR
License: GPL-2

